latestIgtvVideos.title: In frame @wheresnikkigoing
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Posted @withregram • @wheresnikkigoing Here's my first MAKEUP VIDEO guys!!! Tap the ❤️ and show some love! 

Created these 2 looks( office look and party look) using the latest range of Miss Claire Cosmetics which are ridiculously affordable!  Here are my top favs from their range: 

1. Eyeshadow Palette
When it comes to eyeshadow palettes, I end up using and depleting only one or 2 colors (all colors don't suit my desi skintone) and the rest go waste. But here since the colors not only  compliment my Indian skin tone ( warm shades and undertones)but are deeply pigmented and last all day, I'll be using most of the palette. So yaay!!

2. Miss Claire Lipcote 💋
I love my matte lipsticks but frankly getting a new glossy for each shade is a waste of money (not to mention space when I pack my makeup kit). This lipcote💄is an uber cool versatile product that it's packed/applied like a nailpaint💅 & glosses over EVERY matte shade.❤️❤️❤️

3. Anti-Redness Primer 
Yes,  the foundations are creamy, lightweight and blend effortlessly but Primer steals the show!! I've got oily skin and no matter the weather this primer is my ride or die. 

Mua @makeoversbykomalgupta
